				<a href="details" class="propsnapshot"><img src="http://lorempixel.com/205/205/sports/6"><span class="summary"><span class="locked">#163290</span><br>Asking for: <strong>$500,000</strong><br />Revenues: <span style="color: black">$300,000</span>/yr<br />Expenses: <span style="color: red">$100,000</span>/yr</span></a>
