				<a href="details" class="propsnapshot"><img src="http://lorempixel.com/205/205/sports/8"><span class="summary"><span class="locked">#028758</span><br>Asking for: <strong>$4,000,000</strong><br />Revenues: <span style="color: black">$500,000</span>/yr<br />Expenses: <span style="color: red">$100,000</span>/yr</span></a>
